The sudden death
of the Second Young Master

00:39:35.950 --> 00:39:37.800
has been pinned on Mr. Qin.

00:39:38.150 --> 00:39:39.710
In truth, it's because his reforms

00:39:39.710 --> 00:39:41.000
affected family interests.

00:39:41.400 --> 00:39:42.800
After returning home yesterday,

00:39:42.800 --> 00:39:44.320
